\begin_inset Formula $s_{1},s_{2},\ldots,s_{p}$
\end_inset

 are the scale factors of the similitudes of the IFS of a rep-tile, then
 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{1}^{2}+s_{2}^{2}+\cdots+s_{p}^{2}=1$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

