\begin_inset Formula $s<1$
\end_inset

 such that
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{d(T(\mathbf{x}),T(\mathbf{y}))}{d(\mathbf{x},\mathbf{y})}\leq s.
\]

\end_inset

A contraction mapping scales down the distance between every pair of distinct
